{"tid":323124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅會指血庫存量偏低 O+型為甚","createTime":"2017-07-15T11:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T12:38:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69452f527110f30fe9bbc2454709b5e90155ecf2","tid":323124,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"香港紅十字會輸血服務中心公佈，周五只有835人捐血，成功收集638袋血液。由於現時血液需求持續高企，血庫存量已下降至偏低水平，特別是O正型血液，中心呼籲市民今個周末捐血。<br />\n<br />\n中心指每日要1,100人捐血，才能夠保障全港醫院有足夠的血液，為病人輸血，但近期捐血人數一直未能達標，加上夏季流感高峰期提早來臨，令公立醫院急症室及內科病房使用率急增。"},{"pid":"371da147ffa5e6cc4e10aeb37ce7ef65ae1335c5","tid":323124,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 一個JR 鍵盤捐血都係番晒度啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b861cd92964c561bd1e2c5a7f2c29aa35af7cd2","tid":323124,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"月經，血用左去邊，有無完整百份比？"},{"pid":"ac3a6bda489a8ba33e00e0b3e93f07ebedc8b940","tid":323124,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d6a1e99998687724937d99abacd805160992404","tid":323124,"uid":29076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"我係O+喎<br />\n唔捐"},{"pid":"06aa5f4a011fac0674ab966565882af4ef08322d","tid":323124,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係O+喎<br />\n唔捐</blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"af77a84be001ff8fab4cfafbbe6aa9d189db7b07","tid":323124,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔緊要啦 一個JR 鍵盤捐血都係番晒度啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又想係到盲目鼓吹唔捐血?</blockquote><br />\n你咪第一個帶頭唔捐果個囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3eee49da2ee275acb